\c 150
\s Dumisani iN\nd kosi\nd*
\p
\v 1 Dumisani iN\nd kosi\nd*! Dumisani uNkulunkulu endlini yakhe engcwele\x + Hlab. 11.4.\x*; mdumiseni emkhathini wamandla akhe\x + Hlab. 68.34.\x*.
\v 2 Mdumiseni ngenxa yezenzo zakhe ezilamandla\x + Dute. 3.24.\x*\x + Hlab. 145.12.\x*, limdumise ngenxa yobunengi bobukhulu bakhe\x + Dute. 3.24.\x*.
\v 3 Mdumiseni ngokuvuthelwa kophondo, limdumise\x + Hlab. 11.4.\x* ngogubhu lwezintambo\x + Hlab. 149.3. Hlab. 71.22.\x* lechacho\x + Hlab. 149.3. Hlab. 71.22.\x*,
\v 4 limdumise\x + Hlab. 149.3. Hlab. 71.22.\x* ngesigujana langokusina\x + Eks. 15.20.\x*, limdumise ngezinto zokuhlabelela ezilentambo\x + Isa. 38.20.\x* langomhlanga\x + Gen. 4.21. Jobe 21.12. 30.31.\x*,
\v 5 limdumise ngensimbi ezincencethayo ezihlokomayo\x + 2 Sam. 6.5. 1 Lan. 15.16,19,28. 25.1,6.\x*, limdumise ngensimbi ezincencethayo ezikhala kakhulu\x + 2 Sam. 6.5. 1 Lan. 15.16,19,28. 25.1,6.\x*.
\v 6 Konke okuphefumulayo\x + Hlab. 145.21.\x* kakudumise iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Hlab. 68.4.\x*. Dumisani iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Hlab. 41.13. 105.45.\x*!